Looking at your files, I understand your current implementation. Since the new requirement is:

1. Customer exists only / account not found → registrationId, subscriptionId, accountNumber = null


2. Customer + account exists → return all 3 fields.


3. Subscription has >500 accounts → registrationId, accountNumber, subscriptionId = null



you should not use a single JOIN query anymore. The service should control the flow.


